portals</li><li>Custom themes &amp; plugin development</li><li>SEO-friendly and mobile-responsive layouts</li><li>Speed optimization &amp; security hardening</li><li>Ongoing maintenance &amp; support</li></ul><p><strong>Technology Requirements (WordPress)</strong></p><ul><li>PHP 7.4+</li><li>MySQL / MariaDB</li><li>Apache or Nginx Server</li><li>HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript</li><li>WordPress Core &amp; REST API</li><li>Popular Plugins (WooCommerce, Elementor, Yoast, etc.)</li><li>Git version control (optional)</li><li>Hosting (Shared / VPS / Cloud)</li></ul><h3>Shopify Development</h3><p>Shopify is a robust eCommerce platform designed for fast, secure, and scalable online stores.</p><p><strong>What we deliver</strong></p><ul><li>Custom Shopify store setup &amp; configuration</li><li>Theme customization &amp; UI enhancements</li><li>Shopify app integration &amp; custom features</li><li>Payment gateway &amp; shipping setup</li><li>Store optimization for performance &amp; conversions</li><li>Store maintenance &amp; product management</li></ul><p><strong>Technology Requirements (Shopify)</strong></p><ul><li>Shopify Platform &amp; Admin Panel</li><li>Liquid Template Language</li><li>HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript</li><li>Shopify APIs &amp; Webhooks</li><li>Shopify Apps &amp; Extensions</li><li>Payment Gateway Integration</li><li>Domain &amp; SSL Configuration</li></ul>',NULL,'Jobs',NULL,1,'2026-01-06 18:07:54','2026-01-06 18:07:54'),(47,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'1767736924591.png',NULL,NULL,'UploadImages',NULL,1,'2026-01-06 22:02:04','2026-01-06 22:02:04'),(70,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'1767741125531.png',NULL,NULL,'images',NULL,1,'2026-01-06 23:12:05','2026-01-06 23:12:05'),(71,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'1767741200461.png',NULL,NULL,'images',NULL,1,'2026-01-06 23:13:20','2026-01-06 23:13:20'),(73,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'1767742545618.png',NULL,NULL,'images',NULL,1,'2026-01-06 23:35:45','2026-01-06 23:35:45'),(77,'Empowering Your Business with End-to-End Custom Web Experiences','',NULL,NULL,NULL,'1767773217249.png','<p>At <strong>PARAKSHTECH</strong>, we deliver <strong>end-to-end web development solutions</strong> tailored to meet your business goals. We help startups, SMEs, and enterprises build powerful digital experiences that drive growth, engagement, and long-term success.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h4>Technologies We Work With</h4><p>HTML • CSS • JavaScript • PHP • Java • React.js • Node.js</p>','<p>Collaborate with <strong>PARAKSHTECH</strong> to experience cutting-edge web development services that ensure <strong>flexibility, security, scalability, and exceptional user experience</strong>. Our proven expertise and innovative approach have delivered outstanding results for clients across industries.</p><h4>&nbsp;</h4><h4><strong>Our Web Development Services</strong></h4><h4>1. PHP Web Development</h4><p>PHP is a powerful open-source technology supporting platforms like <strong>Windows, Linux, UNIX, and Solaris</strong>. Our expert PHP developers leverage modern frameworks and best practices to build secure, scalable, and high-performance web applications.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h4>2. .NET Web Development</h4><p>ASP.NET is a fast, reliable, and robust framework for building dynamic web applications. Our skilled .NET developers create feature-rich, user-friendly websites with excellent performance and seamless functionality.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h4>3. Frontend &amp; Framework Development&nbsp;</h4><ul><li>Bootstrap Development</li><li>AngularJS Development</li><li><p>React.js Development</p><p>&nbsp;</p></li></ul><h4>4. Backend Development</h4><ul><li>PHP Development</li><li>Java Development</li><li><p>Node.js Development</p><p>&nbsp;</p></li></ul><h4>5. CMS Development</h4><ul><li>WordPress Development</li><li>Laravel Development</li><li>CodeIgniter Development</li></ul>','Web Development','\"<h4><strong>End-to-End Web Development for Customized Business Solutions</strong></h4><p><strong>PARAKSHTECH</strong> is a leading web development company offering a wide range of services including <strong>eCommerce Development, CMS Development, PHP, Java, and .NET Web Solutions</strong>.</p><p>In today’s competitive digital landscape, having a modern, high-performance website is essential for business growth and online visibility. Our team of experienced developers uses the <strong>latest and most preferred web technologies</strong> to ensure your website stands out from the competition.</p><p>We focus on:</p><ul><li>Advanced functionality implementation</li><li>Modern frameworks and scalable architecture</li><li>Extensive testing and performance optimization</li><li>Secure, flexible, and high-quality solutions</li></ul><p>An up-to-date website not only strengthens your brand presence but also helps you outperform competitors</p>\"',1,'2026-01-07 08:06:57','2026-01-07 08:06:57'),(79,'','','Web Development',NULL,'','1767774611300.png','',NULL,'ValuedServices',NULL,1,'2026-01-07 08:30:11','2026-01-07 08:30:11'),(80,'','','Software Development',NULL,'','1767774688136.png','',NULL,'ValuedServices',NULL,1,'2026-01-07 08:31:28','2026-01-07 08:31:28'),(81,'','','App Development',NULL,'','1767774723460.png','',NULL,'ValuedServices',NULL,1,'2026-01-07 08:32:03','2026-01-07 08:32:03'),(82,'','','Web Designing',NULL,'','1767774778136.png','',NULL,'ValuedServices',NULL,1,'2026-01-07 08:32:58','2026-01-07 08:32:58'),(83,'','','Digital Marketing',NULL,'','1767774840551.png','',NULL,'ValuedServices',NULL,1,'2026-01-07 08:34:00','2026-01-07 08:34:00'),(84,'','','E-Commerce Solutions',NULL,'','1767774893774.png','',NULL,'ValuedServices',NULL,1,'2026-01-07 08:34:53','2026-01-07 08:34:53'),(88,'Software That Transforms Business','',NULL,NULL,NULL,'1767778738365.png','<p>Optimized applications designed to streamline operations and boost ROI</p>','<p>An effective Software application can accomplish various tasks in minutes which would otherwise takes a lot of time. It includes payroll, accounting functions, inventory control, word processing etc. Our team has excellent organisational and time management skills as well as problem solving and curiosity of learning attitude which can be really beneficial for creating software which can increase the productivity of the business.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Process of Software Development</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><ul><li>Analyze</li><li>Design</li><li>Development</li><li>Implement</li></ul>','Software Development','\"<h3><strong>Modern Software Solution Company In Buxar</strong></h3><p>Software Applications are really helpful for business, as they save a lot of time and money. ParakshTech provides custom software solutions across the globe. Our Software Development team always makes sure to cater our client’s needs by offering software applications that are cost-effective and provides value to the business.</p><p><br>Our team of Professional Software Developers always keep them continually updated with advanced technologies, concepts to create effective software in a short span of time. Our main focus is always on developing Software Applications that helps your business become paperless by facilitating the business workflow. We provide cloud based software solution as well business management solutions, ERP and CRM to meet the specific business requirements of the clients.</p>\"',1,'2026-01-07 09:38:58','2026-01-07 09:38:58'),(90,'Mobile App Development You Can Trust','',NULL,NULL,NULL,'1767780165872.png','<p>Full-lifecycle solutions for Android, iOS &amp; cross-platform growth</p>','<p>Our Mobile App Development team always keep them updated with the latest and advanced technologies and resources for developing apps with excellent UI, UX, speed and navigation. We have the experience of creating mobile apps of almost every category ranging from Business, Education, Entertainment, Travel, News etc.&nbsp; With 10+ years of experience in Mobile App development, we have worked with many diverse brands, organisations, startups as well as individuals.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Android App Developmnet –</strong>Android is the most rapidly growing operating system in mobile app technology. Our team of mobile app developers have in depth knowledge of latest android app development techniques. Our Android development team always do extensive research and evaluation before developing the app to make sure it meets the needs and expectations of the client.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>iOS App Development -</strong> iOS mobile applications are loved by mobile phone lovers internationally because of its high quality standards. We create dynamic and feature-enriched iOS applications that works flawlessly.&nbsp; An effective and user friendly mobile app can work as wonder for your business.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>We also assist in these services-</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><ol><li><p><strong>Upgradation and Migration of Mobile App </strong>– We also provide Migration and Upgradation of Mobile Apps for helping the clients meet their specific business requirements.</p><p>&nbsp;</p></li><li><p><strong>Maintenance and App support service</strong>– We provide constant development support to our clients which include maintenance and App support services.</p><p>&nbsp;</p></li><li><p><strong>Secure and High performing apps</strong>– Our team of expert mobile app developers always makes sure to develop secure and high performing Apps.</p><p>&nbsp;</p></li><li><strong>Quality analyses and Testing services-</strong>We also provide quality analyses and testing services during the App development process.</li></ol><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Our Mobile App Development Service includes-</p><p>&nbsp;</p><ul><li>iPhone App Development</li><li>Cross- Platform App Development</li><li>Android App Development</li><li>iPad App Development</li></ul><p>&nbsp;</p>','App Development','\"<h4><strong>Full Cycle Mobile App Development Across Various Platforms</strong></h4><p>The Rise in the Mobile App technology has made the Modern world heavily dependent on Mobile Apps. Many businesses have changed their strategies to use Mobile Apps to gain more customers. &nbsp;The Increasing demand for Android and iOS mobile apps lead to a boom in the Mobile App Industry. ParakshTech is among the best Mobile App development companies serving clients worldwide. At ParakshTech we develop and design Customized, Hybrid as well as Simple Navigation Android and iPhone Mobile Apps with the help of our passionate mobile App developers. &nbsp;Our team of dedicated developers follow a specific pattern before developing a mobile app. It includes understanding the requirements of the client before developing and designing the mobile app. We always focus on building mobile apps that help businesses reach their potential customers and grow their businesses.</p>\"',1,'2026-01-07 10:02:45','2026-01-07 10:02:45'),(91,'Custom Web Designing Excellence','',NULL,NULL,NULL,'1767781489262.png','<p>Tailored designs that reflect your brand, optimize user journey, and grow engagement</p>','<p>We always try to focus on these aspects of the website.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Responsive Websites</strong>– We always designs Responsive Website that adjusts themselves according to the device’s screen dimensions. For ideal viewing, the website is optimized in such a way so that it can be easily fit to screen size of any device from a smartphone, tablet, desktop or laptop.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Customized Website</strong>– We design customized websites that can be easily changed or modified without changing the code.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Our team of web designers have designed a variety of websites for &nbsp;a number of clients globally.&nbsp; We always make sure to design professional, custom-friendly, easy to navigate and attractive websites. A well designed and well-optimized website can help convey the idea of business to your potential clients clearly. It can also help attract &nbsp;potential customers and increase &nbsp;sales.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>&nbsp;We are specialised in-</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><ul><li>Layout Design</li><li>UI/UX</li><li>Usability</li><li>Interaction</li><li>Responsive Design</li><li>HTML5</li></ul>','Web Designing','\"<h4><strong>Innovative Web Designing For Creating User Friendly Interfaces</strong></h4><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The Design of the website is the first thing that the user notices whenever he visits the website. That is the reason why it is really important to have an aesthetically pleasing website.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;At ParakshTech we aim at Designing Attractive and Informative websites. As a professional Web Design company, we have a complete understanding of the business requirements and attractive web designs. We always target to create visually engaging, customized, responsive and easy to navigate websites for meeting the business objectives of our clients. Our team of experienced web designers are really efficient in HTML5, CSS3 and Flat UI tools to create attractive and informative web designs. We always make sure that every web page on the website has an exceptional and appealing layout that helps add value to your business.</p>\"',1,'2026-01-07 10:24:49','2026-01-07 10:24:49'),(92,'Performance-Focused Digital Marketing','',NULL,NULL,NULL,'1767783167944.png','<p>Strategies tailored for growth, visibility, and lasting customer engagement</p>','<p>As a renowned Digital Marketing Company, we serve clients in over 90+ countries. Our Digital Marketing campaign also includes social media plans, Innovative designs etc. &nbsp;If you want to grab more users to your website and boost revenues, ParakshTech is always ready to assist you with its creative and experienced Digital Marketing team.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Our Primary Digital Marketing Services –</p><p>&nbsp;</p><ol><li><p><strong>Search Engine Optimization (SEO)- </strong>For Generating enough traffic and leads, your website needs to be positioned on the first pages of the search results (SERPs). Our SEO team follows an effective strategy for making your business website rank higher in the search results. Our strategy includes analysis of the website, Keyword Research, On-Page and Off-page SEO as well as website performance evaluation.</p><p>&nbsp;</p></li><li><strong>Social Media Marketing(SMM)-</strong>Social Media Marketing nowadays is &nbsp;beneficial in facilitating your business growth. Our skilful Digital Marketing team is capable of handling all your social media pages including Facebook, Twitter, Instagram, LinkedIn etc. which can lead to an increase in the number of the users on the website.</li></ol>','Digital Marketing','\"<h4><strong>Enhance Engagements With Our Digital Marketing That Works</strong></h4><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Let us help bring traffic to your website and grow your online business with the Digital Marketing services of ParakshTech. Our Digital marketing team always ensure that your website gets enough traffic to help your business reach greater heights.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Our complete Digital Marketing Solutions includes SEO Services, Social Media Marketing, Email Marketing, Content Marketing, Mobile App Marketing, Online Reputation Marketing. Our team always analyze client’s needs as well as search behaviour of potential users before implementing the solution for increasing leads, sales and ultimately revenue for the business.</p>\"',1,'2026-01-07 10:52:47','2026-01-07 10:52:47'),(93,'Custom Ecommerce Website Development','',NULL,NULL,NULL,'1767786022537.png','<h4>Build and grow your online store with our professional ecommerce solutions. We design secure, scalable, and high-performing ecommerce websites.&nbsp;</h4>','<ul><li><strong>Ecommerce Platform Development: </strong>Expert solutions for Shopify, WooCommerce, Magento, and custom-built platforms<strong>.</strong></li><li><strong>Payment Gateway Integration: </strong>Secure and smooth online payment systems to enhance user trust and conversion.</li><li><strong>Inventory &amp; Order Management:</strong> Streamlined solutions to manage products, track orders, and control stock efficiently.</li><li><strong>Multi-Vendor Marketplace Development</strong>: Create scalable online marketplaces with vendor dashboards and secure management tools.</li><li><strong>Maintenance &amp; Support:</strong> Ongoing technical support to ensure your ecommerce store performs at its best 24/7.</li></ul><p>&nbsp;</p><h4><strong>Why Choose Us&nbsp;</strong></h4><p>Choosing the right ecommerce partner can make all the difference. Here’s why businesses trust ParakshTech IT Solutions:</p><ul><li><strong>End-to-End Expertise: </strong>From strategy to design, development, and optimization we handle everything.</li><li><strong>Scalable &amp; Secure Solutions:</strong> Our ecommerce systems are designed to grow with your business.</li><li><strong>User-Centric Design: </strong>We focus on intuitive, conversion-optimized experiences that turn visitors into loyal customers.</li><li><strong>Custom Integrations: </strong>Seamless connections with CRMs, ERPs, APIs, and third-party tools.</li><li><strong>Transparent Process: </strong>Clear communication, timely updates, and a dedicated project team.</li></ul><p>&nbsp;</p><h4><strong>Technologies We Use&nbsp;</strong></h4><p>We leverage the latest ecommerce technologies and frameworks to build reliable, high-performing online stores.</p><ul><li><strong>Platforms:</strong> Shopify, WooCommerce, Magento, OpenCart, PrestaShop</li><li><strong>Front-End: </strong>React, Angular, Vue.js</li><li><strong>Back-End: </strong>Node.js, Laravel, PHP, Python</li><li><strong>Databases: </strong>MySQL, MongoDB, Firebase</li><li><strong>Payment &amp; APIs: </strong>Stripe, PayPal, Razorpay, RESTful &amp; GraphQL APIs</li></ul><p>&nbsp;</p><h4><strong>Our Process&nbsp;</strong></h4><ul><li>We understand your business goals and create a custom strategy.</li><li>Interactive, responsive designs crafted for a seamless user experience.</li><li>Scalable backend architecture and feature-rich front-end.</li><li>Thorough performance, usability, and security testing.</li><li>Smooth deployment with post-launch optimization and maintenance.</li></ul><p>&nbsp;</p><h4><strong>E-commerce Platforms We Specialize In&nbsp;</strong></h4><p>We work with a variety of e-commerce platforms to provide scalable and high-performance online stores tailored to your business model and goals. Whether you need a simple store setup or a complex multi-vendor marketplace, our experts create the right solution for you.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h4><strong>Our Expertise Includes:</strong></h4><ul><li><strong>Shopify Development: </strong>Create fast, secure, and conversion-driven online stores.</li><li><strong>WooCommerce Development</strong>: Powerful ecommerce solutions seamlessly integrated with WordPress.</li><li><strong>Magento Development</strong>: Enterprise-level ecommerce development for high-traffic businesses.</li><li><strong>Custom Ecommerce Solutions</strong>: Tailored ecommerce platforms built from scratch to match your business needs.</li></ul>','Ecommerce Solutions','\"<h4><strong>Build, Scale &amp; Transform Your Online Store with Expert Ecommerce Solutions</strong>&nbsp;</h4><p>We help businesses launch and grow powerful online stores that drive sales and deliver seamless shopping experiences. From intuitive website design to advanced ecommerce integrations, we provide end-to-end solutions that make your online business thrive in the digital marketplace.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h4><strong>Our Ecommerce Solutions&nbsp;</strong></h4><p>We offer a complete suite of ecommerce development services designed to meet the unique needs of every business whether you’re starting from scratch or upgrading an existing store.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><ul><li><strong>Custom Ecommerce Website Development: </strong>Tailored online stores built to reflect your brand identity and business goals.</li></ul>\"',1,'2026-01-07 11:40:22','2026-01-07 11:40:22');
